The Original Moon & Smashing Pumpkins Demo Tapes sold at early shows.

Digitaly Remastered!

Tracks 1-6 is the self-released tape called Smashing Pumpkins and was sold at early shows. Info from inside the sleeve: Produced by Wuentin Sanbria and Billy Corgan. Engineered by Paul Chabala. Recorded at Schwa Production. (C) copyright 1989 the smashing pumpkins. 
DOR: 1989/03/28 (USA). Pressing info: 500 cassettes with white paper j-card & handwritten lables.

Tracks 7-19 is the self-released tape called Moon and was sold at early shows for $5. Info from the inside sleeve: Produced by Billy Corgan. Engineered by Mark Ingoffo. At Reel Time Studios. Mark also plays organ. All songs by Corgan except Stars Fall In by Corgan/Iha and Daughter by Corgan/Wretzky (C) 1989 the smashing pumpkins.
DOR: 1989 (USA). Pressing info: 500 cassettes with white paper j-card & handwritten labels.
